== Installing Linphone from scratch ==

Generate:
autogen
automake 1.9+
autoconf
libtool

Configure:
intltool
exosip
osip
speex-dev
speexdsp-dev (opt)

hardcode error:
readline5-dev

install libgsm to hear voice prompts in gsm format

install ffmpeg from source:
libvorbis-dev (to be stripped)
./configure --enable-shared --enable-swscale --enable-gpl
